snippet.title: Prospector  - Teaser Trailer Pre Alpha
snippet.description:
Wishlist Prospector now on Steam! 
🕹️ https://bit.ly/35P5Lg9 

Prospector is a 2D open world adventure made with hand-crafted pixel art and synthwave vibes. Start with nothing, then build an outpost to survive any hostile entities you encounter while exploring a dangerous alien ecosystem. Uncover its ancient secrets and build some robot friends to aid in your quest to tame this uncharted landscape and find a way home.
